# Obsidian Hotkeys
## Most Important Hotkeys
- 'ctrl + p' open command pallette
- 'ctrl +o' to open quick switcher
- 'ctrl + n' create a new default note
- 'alt + n' create a new note from template
- 'alt + f' create a new note in folder
- 'alt + e' insert template
- 'ctrl + d' open daily note
- 'ctrl + w' open weekly note
- 'ctrl + s' search
- 'ctrl + tab' go to next tab
- 'ctrl + enter' open link under cursor in new tab
- 'ctrl + alt +enter' open link under cursor to the right
- 'shift + right arrow' split right
- 'shift + down arrow' split down
- 'ctrl + m' move to folder
- 'ctrl + r'  rename file
- 'ctrl + h' file and replace in current file
- 'ctrl + ;' add file properties
- 'ctrl + shift + i' open console (error log)
- 'alt + p' show properties view
## Quick Add
- 'alt + t' add to task list
- 'alt + q' add to quick note
- 'alt + h' add to What's Happening
- 'alt + m' add to meeting agenda
## Formatting
- 'alt + c' to add a callout
- 'alt + s' superscript
- 'ctrl + b' bold
- 'ctrl + i' italic
## Move
- 'alt + 1' to move a line of text up.
- 'alt + 2' to move a line of text down.
- 'tab' to indent text.
- 'shift + tab' to outdent.
- 'alt + f' to fold text.
- 'alt + b' bullet/checkbox
